\because & f(0)=b
\end{array}
$$<br/><br/>
Now, $\lim _\limits{x \rightarrow 0^{-}} f(x)=\lim _\limits{x \rightarrow 0^{-}}\left(\frac{\sin (a+1) x+\sin 2 x}{2 x}\right)$<br/><br/>
